snippet: Clashes between security forces and antigovernment protesters on the third anniversary of the nation’s uprising left dozens wounded, the authorities and activists said Friday.
abstract: Clashes between Bahraini security forces and antigovernment protesters on the third anniversary of the nation's uprising leaves dozens wounded.
